      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "## 🚨 PII Offenders & Data-Theft Watch\n\nWho's pasting credit cards, asking for mass employee/customer exports, and tripping the data-exfiltration alert. **Tim Heidecker** (and Eric to a lesser extent) should dominate every panel — they're the loadgen archetypes for the data-thief story.\n\n**Demo flow:**\n1. Open this tab — see Tim at the top of the offender rankings already populated by loadgen\n2. **Last 10 credit-card pastes** shows masked last-4s only — visibility without leaking\n3. **Data-theft alert state** flips to FIRING when an employee fires 5+ exfil-shaped events in 10 min (Tim trips this every ~3-5 minutes of loadgen runtime)\n4. **Email sent** counts the security@acme.local notifications routed by the alert",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "grafanacloud-logs"
      },
      "description": "Fires when any single user crosses 5 exfil-shaped events in 10m.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "mappings": [
            {
              "options": {
                "0": {
                  "color": "green",
                  "text": "OK"
                }
              },
              "type": "value"
            },
            {
              "options": {
                "from": 1,
                "result": {
                  "color": "red",
                  "text": "🔥 FIRING"
                },
                "to": 999
              },
              "type": "range"
            }
          ],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": 1
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 8
      },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "grafanacloud-logs"
          },
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({namespace=\"supportbot\"} |~ \"alert: name=data_theft state=firing\" [10m])) or vector(0)",
